comments: Biyombo (CHA) establishes a legal guarding position on Anunoby (TOR) and does not move into his path to impede him.
Siakam (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Graham (CHA) and absorbs the contact.
Boucher (TOR) sets the screen in Rozier's (CHA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Washington (CHA) jumps from A to B into Boucher's (TOR) body and affects his shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) sets the screen on Graham (CHA) and does not deliver contact.
Rozier (CHA) moves laterally into Lowry's (TOR) path and initiates contact that affects his shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) extends his forearm into Graham's (CHA) chest and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Hawyward (CHA) sets the screen on Lowry (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact with Hayward (CHA) as he establishes a post position. Hayward's momentum is moving in the direction of the contact when it occurs.
Graham (CHA) gathers the ball and takes two steps before fumbling the ball. He gathers the fumble and does not move his pivot foot before shooting.
Johnson (TOR) makes marginal contact with Graham (CHA) at the start of his drive.
Johnson (TOR) legally contests Graham's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
Rozier (CHA) commits a take foul on VanVleet (TOR).
Ball (CHA) makes marginal contact with Siakam (TOR) as he makes the pass.
Rozier (CHA) commits a take foul on Boucher (TOR).
Biyombo (CHA) sets the screen in Siakam's (TOR) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Johnson (TOR) jumps towards Rozier (CHA) and makes contact with his lower body during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
